# Album Workspace Rules

Index: `02_albums/README.md`. New album: copy `_album_template/` → `02_albums/<slug>/`.

## Input folder

`input/` — user drops raw text here. Orchestrator reads only (see `input/README.md`, `/orchestrate album`).

## Active album minimum

Always keep current: `album.md`, `track_map.md`, `conclusions/album_direction_decisions.md`.

## Track folder (`tracks/<slug>/`)

Develop **one track at a time**. Status in `track.md` / `track_map.md`:

`idea` → `pool` → `briefed` → `lyrics` → `suno` → `shortlist` → `final` | `cut` | `hold`

## Final track archive

Must have: `song_brief.md`, `lyrics/lyrics_final.md`, `suno/final_suno_fields.md`, `metadata/final_style.md`, `metadata/track_metadata.md`, `analysis/final_selection_reason.md`, final audio in `audio/`.

## One source of truth

- Final lyrics → `lyrics_final.md` only (don't duplicate across files).
- Link audio ↔ prompt version ↔ listening notes.
- Link to `album.md` / dossier — don't paste full album docs into track files.

After meaningful sessions: update status fields, `track_map.md`, extract learnings to `learnings/` or `03_global_learnings/` if reusable.
